{"tid":631301,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"★大師神喻：4月16日----4月20日","createTime":"2018-04-16T10:51:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-19T12:24:21.000Z","uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"2d047e457adc453cf2205d1bf74dcdf26712c071","tid":631301,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T10:51:33.000Z","msg":"周一(戊寅日)：天干屬土地支屬木，木剋土之局，大市出現震盪。<br />\n<br />\n周二(己卯日)：天干屬土地支屬木，木剋土之局，持續震盪。<br />\n<br />\n周三(庚辰日)：天干屬金地支屬土，土生金之局，出現反彈。<br />\n<br />\n周四(辛巳日)：天干屬金地支屬火，火剋金之局，反覆徘徊。<br />\n<br />\n周五(壬午日)：天干屬水地支屬火，水火交戰之局，波動而乏方向。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://money18.on.cc/econ/content.html?section=mktcomm&amp;article_id=bkn-20180416000000574-0416_00842_001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmoney18.on.cc%2Fecon%2Fcontent.html%3Fsection%3Dmktcomm%26article_id%3Dbkn-20180416000000574-0416_00842_001&d=4FvlyEH6dK%2B%2FrrW2fqsZeARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=2ebc4011\" target=\"_blank\">http://money18.on.cc/econ/content.html?section=mktcomm&amp;article_id=bkn-20180416000000574-0416_00842_001</a>"},{"pid":"aa790a766b24f54015e6799a147c0a4b09e19e7f","tid":631301,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T10:52:32.000Z","msg":"周一(戊寅日)：天干屬土地支屬木，木剋土之局，<span style=\"color: red;\">大市出現震盪。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64427402ec0decbdd5b0bac4b3ac786039032c91","tid":631301,"uid":173326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"aa790a766b24f54015e6799a147c0a4b09e19e7f","tid":631301,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T10:52:32.000Z","msg":"周一(戊寅日)：天干屬土地支屬木，木剋土之局，<span style=\"color: red;\">大市出現震盪。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T11:06:47.000Z","msg":"咁聽日咪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7adb45b025fcb86b244b89cd14754f83f0b2854","tid":631301,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T11:09:03.000Z","msg":"Old cat<br />\nWhy you are here<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd2867411f54154a28d9ed620a52056b013ab301","tid":631301,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T11:17:29.000Z","msg":"港股向下隊，全日大跌近500點。訊匯證券行政總裁「沈大師」認為，大市向下，主要受累兩大因素，一方面受港匯捱沽所累，另外A股見弱。<br />\n他指，「通常夜晚（金管局）仲接得多，你見兩次接錢，一次係11點幾，一次係零晨1點幾，歐美時段啲錢係套得多。今日晏畫已接30幾億，如果今晚再接多30至60億，咁嘅速度去，只會越來越快。」<br />\n另一方面，「A股表現比較差，似乎A股會有因素出緊嚟，但唔知咩知。內銀股係咁跌落去。26隻內銀A股全部都跌，建行（939）跌4%，工行（1398）跌超過3%；內銀H股都跌，咁會唔會有啲政策，或者資金鏈嘅因素我唔知啦。」<br />\n他強調，「要繼續一股不留，唔好去博反彈，進取嘅你可以順住個勢造淡倉，一抽高就沽。」他指，自己100%揸淡倉；港股方面，大師一如早前所指，「熊市仍然係八成機會。」<br />\n騰訊（700）方面，自沈大師於黃大仙廟求得一支下下籤「岳飛遇害」後，月線圖自農曆年後，已連續出現三支「下下籤」（三連陰）。沈大師指，繼大股東沽貨、業績遊戲業務未如理想後，摩根大通有約390億港元騰訊淡倉，成為騰訊捱打的「第三道金牌」。<br />\n「遲啲會唔會有啲大行報告要Downgrade佢，呢啲就跟住嚟；應該如無意外仲有啲係政策面嘅嘢，遲啲第三支付應該會有政策，阻礙到佢呢方面增長動力。」"},{"pid":"2d836d3d86ac36fe273f3d1e7bb06e15b43fc9a3","tid":631301,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64427402ec0decbdd5b0bac4b3ac786039032c91","tid":631301,"uid":173326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"aa790a766b24f54015e6799a147c0a4b09e19e7f","tid":631301,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T10:52:32.000Z","msg":"周一(戊寅日)：天干屬土地支屬木，木剋土之局，<span style=\"color: red;\">大市出現震盪。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T11:06:47.00